ode to my father ( hangul : &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; ; rr : &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; ; lit . " ode to my father " ) is a 2014 south korean drama film directed by yoon &lt;unk&gt; . it was selected as the south korean entry for the best foreign language film at the 87th academy awards , but was not nominated .